text: Input/Output Data The input/output data is the type of data that an agent expects to receive and deliver. The agent expects UDRs of the type configured in the agent. and it can deliver UDRs of the type configured in the agent, or type: LookupFailure See Data Masking UDRs for further information. MIM The Data Masking agent does not have any agent-specific MIM parameters. For information about the MIM and a list of the general MIM parameters, see Administration and Management in Legacy Desktop .
